<div>The Websites may contain links to third parties’ websites. Please note that HSP is not responsible for the collection, use, maintenance, sharing, or disclosure of data and information by such third parties. If you provide information directly to such sites, the privacy policy and terms of service on those sites are applicable and HSP is not responsible for the information processing practices or privacy policies of such sites.</div>

